      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the outline. Can you actually write out a couple of paragraphs for the middle section? I want it to sound really authoritative and hit hard on why the \"meritocracy\" argument used by critics is basically just a way to ignore the actual historical reality of how wealth was built. Make it sound like it's an undeniable fact rather than just one side of a debate.",
